136
00:10:29,990 --> 00:10:31,550
Are you serious?

137
00:10:37,950 --> 00:10:39,620
Well then...

138
00:10:39,620 --> 00:10:41,720
Togusa, take care of the rest.

139
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,090
Okay.

140
00:10:43,680 --> 00:10:44,830
Let's go.

141
