145
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:04,950
Hey, Isaac! {zomg awesome}

146
00:12:04,950 --> 00:12:06,870
Yeah, Miria?

147
00:12:07,250 --> 00:12:10,500
Are they members of the Dollars too?

148
00:12:10,810 --> 00:12:13,330
Precisely, Miria!

149
00:12:15,180 --> 00:12:17,460
All right, listen up.

150
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:22,470
Now we're part of the group the kids talk about!

151
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:24,050
What the hell?!

152
00:12:24,050 --> 00:12:26,470
Don't tell me they're all...

153
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:29,250
No way! You've got to be kidding me!

154
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:32,620
And! We just met for the first time like, today!

155
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,850
Wowzers!

156
00:12:33,850 --> 00:12:39,450
Wowzers! Wowzers!

157
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:50,830
The sky in my hometown was vast.

158
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:54,800
However, there was nothing.

159
00:12:58,150 --> 00:13:01,810
When I was a kid, this town was full of adventures.

160
00:13:02,330 --> 00:13:05,680
I wonder when I started feeling like this.

161
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:10,100
I wanted to change something.

162
00:13:10,540 --> 00:13:14,120
But I didn't have a reason or the courage.

163
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,600
It was around that time...

164
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:34,960
Uh... Double-click...

165
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:41,190
With a few clicks, a whole new realm opened its gates to me.

166
00:13:42,170 --> 00:13:45,670
An arcane realm that I had been unaware of was within my reach.

167
00:13:47,430 --> 00:13:51,540
I got back in touch with Kida-kun, who had moved to Tokyo.

168
00:13:55,740 --> 00:13:58,440
I even made some new friends.

169
00:13:59,620 --> 00:14:01,890
One night, I had an idea.

170
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:05,490
It started off as a joke though.

171
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:07,050
A gang?

172
00:14:07,050 --> 00:14:07,740
Yes.

173
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:11,950
I hear that Tokyo has lots of gangs.

174
00:14:11,950 --> 00:14:15,040
You're going to create an Internet gang?

175
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:19,210
No, no. I'll make people think it really exists.

176
00:14:19,210 --> 00:14:21,740
Uh, I'll say they're based in Ikebukuro,

177
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:24,250
and spread that rumor on the Net.

178
00:14:24,250 --> 00:14:27,780
We won't say we're in the Dollars.

179
00:14:27,990 --> 00:14:31,670
We'll just start rumors and pretend we heard them from someone else,

180
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:33,150
and spread the name of the Dollars that way.

181
00:14:33,970 --> 00:14:36,460
I even made a webpage for it,

182
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:38,350
and protected it with a password.

183
00:14:38,780 --> 00:14:42,300
I leaked the password through email and BBSes.

184
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:47,800
I also pretended to be a member and made fake posts on BBSes.

185
00:14:48,060 --> 00:14:50,800
Of course, most people didn't believe it.

186
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:53,780
Soon, there were people supporting us.

187
00:14:54,570 --> 00:14:57,010
Everyone was having fun.

188
00:14:58,300 --> 00:15:00,850
But I had a bad feeling.

189
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:13,010
People who called themselves "Dollars" started appearing.

190
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:14,890
That wasn't all.

191
00:15:16,540 --> 00:15:19,350
Before I knew it, there were a lot of new members.

192
00:15:20,430 --> 00:15:23,400
Even though we stopped giving the password out,

193
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:27,900
it seemed like someone on the inside was leaking it.

194
00:15:29,260 --> 00:15:31,360
Guys, can you see this?

195
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:32,360
Hello?

196
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,360
Maybe they got scared.
Hello?

197
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:33,950
Maybe they got scared.

198
00:15:33,950 --> 00:15:37,580
