199
00:15:42,070 --> 00:15:44,230
Even so, I didn't stop.

200
00:15:44,230 --> 00:15:46,540
No, I couldn't stop.

201
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:50,800
I don't really know why.

202
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:54,150
That's not true!

203
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:56,340
There might be some bad people,

204
00:15:56,340 --> 00:15:59,560
but they're not all jerks.

205
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:04,040
Why don't we turn it into a group of decent people?

206
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:08,860
Like doing good deeds to outweigh the bad things.

207
00:16:13,070 --> 00:16:15,600
Like picking up trash,

208
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,330
or erasing graffiti.

209
00:16:24,580 --> 00:16:28,060
The people were astonished.

210
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:33,590
This graffiti was definitely there last night,

211
00:16:33,590 --> 00:16:36,340
but now, it's completely gone.

212
00:16:36,700 --> 00:16:41,660
It's impossible to remove graffiti as large as this on your own.

213
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:43,730
Of course not...
