214
00:16:44,350 --> 00:16:47,230
I came to Tokyo after Kida-kun invited me.

215
00:16:47,230 --> 00:16:47,950
And there...

216
00:16:47,950 --> 00:16:48,770
Dollars?

217
00:16:48,770 --> 00:16:51,860
I don't know the details either,

218
00:16:52,270 --> 00:16:56,870
but they have a lot of members scattered everywhere.

219
00:16:56,870 --> 00:17:00,400
I heard they're one of the color gangs, but no one knows their color.

220
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:02,410
You know the deal with curiosity and the cat.

221
00:17:03,290 --> 00:17:06,290
You shouldn't dig deeper.

222
00:17:06,290 --> 00:17:09,320
But the Dollars are the strongest in the city, right?

223
00:17:09,320 --> 00:17:12,130
So, what kind of gang are the Dollars?

224
00:17:12,130 --> 00:17:15,090
Uh, if I had to describe it...

225
00:17:15,090 --> 00:17:16,300
Colorless?

226
00:17:18,060 --> 00:17:19,220
Dollars?

227
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:20,590
Yeah, I know them.

228
00:17:20,590 --> 00:17:22,810
Well, I'm actually one of them.

229
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:25,600
I got a girlfriend after joining the Dollars!

230
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:28,600
They post crap on BBSes.

231
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:31,110
There's always someone who responds.

232
00:17:31,110 --> 00:17:35,820
Well, once you're an old fart like me, you don't have any other social contact apart from work.

233
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:37,570
Ya know?

234
00:17:37,570 --> 00:17:42,120
The Dollars saved someone who was about to be abducted by kidnappers!

235
00:17:42,450 --> 00:17:43,620
Dollars forever!

236
00:17:45,250 --> 00:17:46,350
So?

237
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:47,850
It's fun, so who cares?

238
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:08,820
This is more fun than I expected.

239
00:18:10,770 --> 00:18:12,830
This is fun.

240
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:18,030
Huh? What?

241
00:18:18,530 --> 00:18:20,490
