243
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:30,210
Do you see an Arabian oil magnate?

244
00:18:30,210 --> 00:18:32,170
Nope.

245
00:18:32,170 --> 00:18:37,430
Togusa-san, the one who responded to us is the real founder, right?

246
00:18:37,430 --> 00:18:40,340
Yeah... I think.

247
00:18:40,340 --> 00:18:42,130
Togusa! The light!

248
00:18:42,130 --> 00:18:44,100
It's red! Red!

249
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:54,840
Pretty talkative, aren't we?

250
00:18:56,190 --> 00:18:58,170
Dotachin! Dotachin!

251
00:18:58,170 --> 00:19:00,110
I told you to stop calling me that.

252
00:19:00,110 --> 00:19:02,950
Someone replied on the Dollars' BBS.

253
00:19:12,820 --> 00:19:14,790
I've made the arrangements.

254
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:16,510
You can meet her.

255
00:19:18,450 --> 00:19:23,260
But in return, I want you to help me.

256
00:19:57,790 --> 00:19:59,050
Celty.

257
00:20:11,870 --> 00:20:12,800
He's gone!

258
00:20:12,800 --> 00:20:14,690
Stop looking around like idiots!

259
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:16,150
Go find him!

260
00:20:16,500 --> 00:20:17,010
Yes ma'am!

261
00:20:17,010 --> 00:20:17,720
Move!

262
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,920
Where did he go?

263
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,050
Damn!

264
00:20:20,050 --> 00:20:20,400
Move!

265
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,500
Enough is enough!

266
00:20:37,860 --> 00:20:38,920
Who's talking?

267
00:20:40,350 --> 00:20:41,920
I don't have a head!

268
00:20:42,270 --> 00:20:43,920
I'm a monster!

269
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:47,680
I don't have a mouth to speak with, nor do I have eyes to show my passion!

270
