Whose voice is this?

272
00:20:50,930 --> 00:20:52,680
So what?

273
00:20:52,970 --> 00:20:55,660
So what?!

274
00:20:56,630 --> 00:20:57,810
Celty...

275
00:21:09,130 --> 00:21:10,990
I'm here.

276
00:21:11,660 --> 00:21:13,930
I do exist!

277
00:21:13,930 --> 00:21:15,190
