278
00:21:20,850 --> 00:21:25,730
If you say I don't have eyes, then behold carefully how I act! {Iunno.  I'll think of something later.}

279
00:21:27,990 --> 00:21:28,620
Die!

280
00:21:28,620 --> 00:21:33,530
Engrave the screams of those who enraged a monster into your mind!

281
00:22:01,380 --> 00:22:04,260
