287
00:22:14,360 --> 00:22:16,140
I'm already screaming.

288
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:17,990
Screaming even louder!

289
00:22:17,990 --> 00:22:20,020
I was born here,

290
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:24,780
in order to engrave my existence into this city!

291
00:22:30,890 --> 00:22:33,410
Are you Ryuugamine Mikado?

292
00:22:37,650 --> 00:22:39,120
Give...

